---
import site from '@/lib/site';
---

<section class="section section--tint s4-process">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="s4-process__intro">
      <h2 class="s4-process__heading">What to Expect During Your NAD+ Injection</h2>
      <p class="s4-process__body">Your appointment is fast, easy, and designed to fit seamlessly into your schedule. Here's how it works at our Millburn spa.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="s4-process__steps">

      <div class="s4-process__step">
        <h3 class="s4-process__step-title">Step 1: Brief Consultation (2-3 minutes)</h3>
        <p class="s4-process__step-body">Your provider will check in with you about your wellness goals and answer any questions. If it's your first NAD+ Injection, we'll explain exactly what to expect.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="s4-process__step">
        <h3 class="s4-process__step-title">Step 2: Quick Injection (1-2 minutes)</h3>
        <p class="s4-process__step-body">The injection itself takes just a minute or two. Most clients describe it as a small pinch. No IV lines, no lengthy sessions. Just a simple shot.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="s4-process__step">
        <h3 class="s4-process__step-title">Step 3: Get Back to Your Day</h3>
        <p class="s4-process__step-body">There's no downtime and no recovery needed. You can return to work, errands, or your daily routine right away. Many clients start noticing more energy and mental clarity within hours.</p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="s4-process__cta">
      <a
        href={site.calcomUrl}
        class="btn btn--primary btn--lg"
      >
        Schedule Now
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .s4-process__intro {
    max-width: var(--container-narrow);
    margin-inline: auto;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .s4-process__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .s4-process__body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .s4-process__steps {
    max-width: var(--container-narrow);
    margin-inline: auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .s4-process__step {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .s4-process__step-title {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: var(--weight-bold);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .s4-process__step-body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .s4-process__cta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .s4-process__cta .btn {
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>
